'''Project for Open Source Media'''

URL = http://posm.tv/

"The Project for Open Source Media is an independent research and development company doing business in three primary areas.

1) The construction and distribution of the Open Media Platform, an open source platform for the development and distribution of next generation television technologies.

2) Providing consulting services to entities wishing to develop next generation television content and applications either on the Open Media Platform or on proprietary platforms such as TiVo and Open TV.

3) The development of next generation television content and applications either on the Open Media Platform or on proprietary platforms."

